# game/Scenes/Bai/BaiDates/baigrottodate.rpy:19
translate portuguese baigrottodate_d3715341:

    # pc "Do you want to come out to a fancy restaurant with me?"
    pc "Queres ir comigo a um restaurante chique?"

# game/Scenes/Bai/BaiDates/baigrottodate.rpy:20
translate portuguese baigrottodate_4243d9c3:

    # pc "It's called The Grotto. It's out on the lake."
    pc "Chama-se A Gruta. Fica junto ao lago."

# game/Scenes/Bai/BaiDates/baigrottodate.rpy:23
translate portuguese baigrottodate_4f7f94cb:

    # bai "Is it expensive?"
    bai "É caro?"

# game/Scenes/Bai/BaiDates/baigrottodate.rpy:24
translate portuguese baigrottodate_3308b177:

    # pc "Pretty expensive, yeah."
    pc "Bastante caro, sim."

# game/Scenes/Bai/BaiDates/baigrottodate.rpy:26
translate portuguese baigrottodate_fb59b9b7:

    # bai "Aw, what the hell. Might as well spend it, right?"
    bai "Ah, que se lixe. Mais vale gastar, certo?"

# game/Scenes/Bai/BaiDates/baigrottodate.rpy:27
translate portuguese baigrottodate_f82e580f:

    # bai "I eat cheap every other day, let's get some fancy food!"
    bai "Como comida barata dia sim, dia não, vamos comer algo sofisticado!"

# game/Scenes/Bai/BaiDates/baigrottodate.rpy:28
translate portuguese baigrottodate_5f71dc40:

    # pc "All right! I'll text you the address and meet you out there."
    pc "Tudo bem! Mando-te a morada por mensagem e encontro-te lá."

# game/Scenes/Bai/BaiDates/baigrottodate.rpy:29
translate portuguese baigrottodate_1bda0dbe:

    # bai "Sounds good! See you there."
    bai "Parece-me ótimo! Vemo-nos lá."

# game/Scenes/Bai/BaiDates/baigrottodate.rpy:32
translate portuguese baigrottodate_cf65d098:

    # "I get ready and text Bai the address, then about an hour later we're sitting down to eat at The Grotto."
    "Preparo-me e mando a morada ao Bai por mensagem; cerca de uma hora depois, estamos sentados a comer no The Grotto."

# game/Scenes/Bai/BaiDates/baigrottodate.rpy:35
translate portuguese baigrottodate_79872e14:

    # bai "That sounds great. Are we going to get all dressed up in suits and stuff?"
    bai "Isso parece ótimo. Vamos vestir-nos todos a rigor, com fatos e assim?"

# game/Scenes/Bai/BaiDates/baigrottodate.rpy:36
translate portuguese baigrottodate_a9dc377e:

    # pc "Damn right, we are."
    pc "Podes crer que sim."

# game/Scenes/Bai/BaiDates/baigrottodate.rpy:38
translate portuguese baigrottodate_bfaba4a8:

    # bai "Oh man. I have to find my suit then. I know I have one in the closet somewhere."
    bai "Caramba. Então tenho de encontrar o meu fato. Sei que tenho um algures no armário."

# game/Scenes/Bai/BaiDates/baigrottodate.rpy:39
translate portuguese baigrottodate_b5cc83ae:

    # bai "I'll go find it."
    bai "Vou procurá-lo."

# game/Scenes/Bai/BaiDates/baigrottodate.rpy:40
translate portuguese baigrottodate_ffb27a81:

    # pc "Okay. Send me a text when you're ready and I'll come pick you up, okay?"
    pc "Está bem. Manda-me uma mensagem quando estiveres pronto e eu vou buscar-te, está bem?"

# game/Scenes/Bai/BaiDates/baigrottodate.rpy:42
translate portuguese baigrottodate_9e815b71:

    # bai "Okay! I'm really excited!"
    bai "Está bem! Estou super entusiasmado!"

# game/Scenes/Bai/BaiDates/baigrottodate.rpy:43
translate portuguese baigrottodate_f07574ec:

    # pc "Good."
    pc "Ótimo."

# game/Scenes/Bai/BaiDates/baigrottodate.rpy:44
translate portuguese baigrottodate_412f6c55:

    # bai "Okay, see you in a bit."
    bai "Está bem, até já."

# game/Scenes/Bai/BaiDates/baigrottodate.rpy:47
translate portuguese baigrottodate_9bcd7a72:

    # "I get ready to go and wait for Bai's text."
    "Preparo-me para sair e fico à espera da mensagem do Bai."

# game/Scenes/Bai/BaiDates/baigrottodate.rpy:48
translate portuguese baigrottodate_9173db50:

    # "About an hour later, he texts me and I go pick him up, then we walk into The Grotto together."
    "Cerca de uma hora depois, ele envia-me uma mensagem e eu vou buscá-lo, depois entramos juntos no The Grotto."

# game/Scenes/Bai/BaiDates/baigrottodate.rpy:51
translate portuguese baigrottodate_9131d6c6:

    # bai "Sounds good! I'll see you there."
    bai "Parece-me bem! Vemo-nos lá."

# game/Scenes/Bai/BaiDates/baigrottodate.rpy:52
translate portuguese baigrottodate_5d3d77d3:

    # pc "Cool. See you."
    pc "Fixe. Até logo."

# game/Scenes/Bai/BaiDates/baigrottodate.rpy:54
translate portuguese baigrottodate_299409d0:

    # bai "That sounds great! I'll start getting ready. Come get me."
    bai "Isso parece-me ótimo! Vou começar a preparar-me. Vem buscar-me."

# game/Scenes/Bai/BaiDates/baigrottodate.rpy:55
translate portuguese baigrottodate_e3948ee8:

    # pc "Alright, I'll be there in a bit."
    pc "Está bem, chego aí daqui a pouco."

# game/Scenes/Bai/BaiDates/baigrottodate.rpy:69
translate portuguese baigrottostartdate_ba211ff8:

    # "We walk in together, holding hands."
    "Entramos juntos, de mãos dadas."

# game/Scenes/Bai/BaiDates/baigrottodate.rpy:70
translate portuguese baigrottostartdate_fb0e2e4f:

    # bai "This feels very public. More public than we usually are."
    bai "Isto parece muito público. Mais público do que costumamos ser."

# game/Scenes/Bai/BaiDates/baigrottodate.rpy:71
translate portuguese baigrottostartdate_a674eec0:

    # pc "Are you okay with that?"
    pc "Não te importas com isso?"

# game/Scenes/Bai/BaiDates/baigrottodate.rpy:72
translate portuguese baigrottostartdate_023cf823:

    # bai "Yeah, with you, I think I am."
    bai "Sim, contigo, acho que não."

# game/Scenes/Bai/BaiDates/baigrottodate.rpy:73
translate portuguese baigrottostartdate_e39c1441:

    # pc "Good. You look like a fucking stud right now. I'm proud to be here with you."
    pc "Ótimo. Pareces um verdadeiro galã neste momento. Tenho orgulho de estar aqui contigo."

# game/Scenes/Bai/BaiDates/baigrottodate.rpy:74
translate portuguese baigrottostartdate_bb37df29:

    # bai "Me too."
    bai "Eu também."

# game/Scenes/Bai/BaiDates/baigrottodate.rpy:81
translate portuguese baigrottostartdate_a5785e55:

    # "We sit at a table and begin looking over the menus."
    "Sentamo-nos à mesa e começamos a dar uma vista de olhos nos menus."

# game/Scenes/Bai/BaiDates/baigrottodate.rpy:82
translate portuguese baigrottostartdate_a395082c:

    # "Then a server comes by and takes our order."
    "Depois, um empregado de mesa aproxima-se e toma o nosso pedido."

# game/Scenes/Bai/BaiDates/baigrottodate.rpy:91
translate portuguese baigrottostartdate_32733c2f:

    # "After we chat for a while, our food is brought out."
    "Depois de conversarmos um pouco, trazem-nos a comida."

# game/Scenes/Bai/BaiDates/baigrottodate.rpy:92
translate portuguese baigrottostartdate_501f942a:

    # bai "Wow, this looks amazing."
    bai "Uau, isto parece incrível."

# game/Scenes/Bai/BaiDates/baigrottodate.rpy:98
translate portuguese baigrottostartdate_28b42b01:

    # "We continue chatting while we eat our meal. Just hanging out and enjoying some good food together."
    "Continuamos a conversar enquanto comemos. Apenas a passar o tempo e a desfrutar de boa comida juntos."

# game/Scenes/Bai/BaiDates/baigrottodate.rpy:101
translate portuguese baigrottostartdate_7150c85d:

    # "When we're done eating, we split the bill and say our goodbyes."
    "Quando terminamos de comer, dividimos a conta e despedimo-nos."

# game/Scenes/Bai/BaiDates/baigrottodate.rpy:105
translate portuguese baigrottostartdate_25d6d119:

    # bai "That was fun, man. Good food. Thanks for inviting me."
    bai "Foi divertido, meu. Boa comida. Obrigado por me convidares."

# game/Scenes/Bai/BaiDates/baigrottodate.rpy:106
translate portuguese baigrottostartdate_0c975e99:

    # pc "No problem. Good to hang out and talk for a while."
    pc "De nada. Foi bom sair e conversar um pouco."

# game/Scenes/Bai/BaiDates/baigrottodate.rpy:107
translate portuguese baigrottostartdate_49b45846:

    # bai "Yeah it was."
    bai "Sim, foi mesmo."

# game/Scenes/Bai/BaiDates/baigrottodate.rpy:108
translate portuguese baigrottostartdate_01c7ca57:

    # bai "Alright, well I'll see you later. Take care."
    bai "Muito bem, então vejo-te mais tarde. Cuida-te."

# game/Scenes/Bai/BaiDates/baigrottodate.rpy:109
translate portuguese baigrottostartdate_22fbafdc:

    # pc "You too. See ya."
    pc "Tu também. Até logo."

# game/Scenes/Bai/BaiDates/baigrottodate.rpy:112
translate portuguese baigrottostartdate_0c8ca28d:

    # "We get in our cars and go our separate directions."
    "Entramos nos nossos carros e seguimos rumos diferentes."

# game/Scenes/Bai/BaiDates/baigrottodate.rpy:120
translate portuguese baigrottostartdate_bfde7d54:

    # "We continue chatting and eating."
    "Continuamos a conversar e a comer."

# game/Scenes/Bai/BaiDates/baigrottodate.rpy:126
translate portuguese baigrottostartdate_1ef0c0b5:

    # "Bai insists that we split the bill, then we get ready to leave."
    "O Bai insiste que dividamos a conta, depois preparamo-nos para sair."

# game/Scenes/Bai/BaiDates/baigrottodate.rpy:132
translate portuguese baigrottostartdate_ca01422f:

    # bai "It's so pretty out here, isn't it?"
    bai "É tão bonito aqui fora, não é?"

# game/Scenes/Bai/BaiDates/baigrottodate.rpy:133
translate portuguese baigrottostartdate_44eeaf1a:

    # pc "Yeah it is."
    pc "Sim, é."

# game/Scenes/Bai/BaiDates/baigrottodate.rpy:139
translate portuguese baigrottostartdate_7c70709c:

    # "I lean in and kiss him, uncaring about anybody who might be watching us."
    "Inclino-me e beijo-o, sem me importar com quem possa estar a observar-nos."

# game/Scenes/Bai/BaiDates/baigrottodate.rpy:140
translate portuguese baigrottostartdate_61700a7a:

    # "He is surprised at first, but doesn't pull away."
    "Ele fica surpreendido no início, mas não se afasta."

# game/Scenes/Bai/BaiDates/baigrottodate.rpy:143
translate portuguese baigrottostartdate_4a0dd6f7:

    # bai "I can't believe I just did that. Right in front of everybody."
    bai "Não acredito que acabei de fazer isso. Mesmo à frente de toda a gente."

# game/Scenes/Bai/BaiDates/baigrottodate.rpy:144
translate portuguese baigrottostartdate_6e718b73:

    # pc "How did it feel?"
    pc "Como te sentiste?"

# game/Scenes/Bai/BaiDates/baigrottodate.rpy:145
translate portuguese baigrottostartdate_3696af55:

    # bai "It felt great."
    bai "Senti-me ótimo."

# game/Scenes/Bai/BaiDates/baigrottodate.rpy:150
translate portuguese baigrottostartdate_d90b231d:

    # bai "Want to go back to my apartment now?"
    bai "Queres ir agora para o meu apartamento?"

# game/Scenes/Bai/BaiDates/baigrottodate.rpy:153
translate portuguese baigrottostartdate_4861bda5:

    # bai "Aw, okay. Well it was a good date, anyway. Thanks for bringing me."
    bai "Ah, está bem. Bem, foi um bom encontro, de qualquer forma. Obrigado por me teres trazido."

# game/Scenes/Bai/BaiDates/baigrottodate.rpy:156
translate portuguese baigrottostartdate_29d9625f:

    # "We leave and I drive him to his aparment and say goodbye."
    "Saímos e levo-o até ao apartamento dele e digo adeus."

# game/Scenes/Bai/BaiDates/baigrottodate.rpy:157
translate portuguese baigrottostartdate_f1413fe1:

    # "Then I drive away to do something else with my night."
    "Depois, vou-me embora para fazer outra coisa esta noite."

# game/Scenes/Bai/BaiDates/baigrottodate.rpy:164
translate portuguese baigrottostartdate_ebdfbc55:

    # "We rush out to the car and drive back to his apartment."
    "Corremos para o carro e voltamos para o apartamento dele."

